10/5(Sat.)Should housewives be paid for their work?/Hangovers are an 'illness,' German court rules(Host:Danny)<br /><br />Article1: Should housewives be paid for their work?<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://gulfnews.com/opinion/letters/should-housewives-be-paid-for-their-work-1.1610254">https://gulfnews.com/opinion/letters/sh ... -1.1610254</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion<br />1. What do you think about that? <br />2. How much money do you think it is reasonable to pay her(or him)?<br />3.I f it can get a salary, are you willing to do this work?<br /><br />Article2: Hangovers are an 'illness,' German court rules<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.dw.com/en/hangovers-are-an-illness-german-court-rules/a-50556379">https://www.dw.com/en/hangovers-are-an- ... a-50556379</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion<br />1. What do you think about the rules?<br />2. Do you have tips to avoid hangover?<br />3. If hangover is a disease, what impact will it have on human society? (Can you take sick leave? According to a Hong Kong report)<br />(<!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://reurl.cc/RdjOa6">https://reurl.cc/RdjOa6</a><!-- m -->)<br /><br />Agenda<br />7:00 ~ 7:30 pm greetings &amp; free talk<br />7:30 ~ 8:15 pm guests introduced &amp; first session discussion<br />8:15 ~ 8:45 pm presentation, sharing the article &amp; other experiences<br />8:45 ~ 9:30 pm second session discussion<br /><br />Position: Dante coffee Shop (丹堤咖啡), MRT板南線 - 新埔站2號出口, next to 7-Seven,<br />板橋民生路二段237 號,<br />Time: PM 7:00-9:30,<br />a minimum charge of Dante coffee for Royal English club attendant NT$80 (丹提低消80元)<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500.請帶著開放與熱情來學英文<br /><br />Royal 三峽 , Royal new branch information,<br />Every Monday evening: 8:00pm- 10pm: 摩斯漢堡 北大特區 土城區學成路712號, next to the park.<br />Please keep contact with President Ophelia.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Sun Sep 29, 2019 11:35 pm</p><hr />
